caption.p: SFE inhibited invasion in H1299 and HCT116 cells. H1299 (a, c) and HCT116 (b) cells were treated with SFE (0–500 μg/ml) for 24 hr. Invasive cells (a, b) and matrix metalloproteinases‐2, 7, 9, and 10 levels (c) were shown as % of control. Different letters (a‐d) indicate significance ( p < .05)
